snippet.title: Frontline Zed - Original Trailer
snippet.description:
Frontline Zed is out NOW on Nintendo Switch!
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/frontline-zed-switch/

And Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/915490/Frontline_Zed/

Join the Official Discord channel to stay up to date with the game and test out new content: https://discord.gg/s3HjzhZ

In the midst of a zombie outbreak, defend your fortified barricade by night, and collect weapons and conduct repairs by day. Survive long enough to make your way through America and towards rescue.

Learn more about Frontline Zed at https://www.frontlinezed.com/
